"{\"uid\": \"pembrokeobserver.com-opinion-columnists-the-valley-pulpit-bizarre-scenes-part-of-opening-ceremony-of-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Something insane happened on the Seine: the opening ceremonies of the 2024 Olympics managed to do major damage to the Olympic brand.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999998831299, \"rank\": 9.912217307046588e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In case you missed it, there were several bizarre scenes, including what looked to be a depiction of the Fourth Horseman of the Revelation (see chapter 6:8).\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The weirdest thing was a tableau that appeared to most observers as a parody of the Last Supper, the meal Jesus shared with his apostles that Christians view as the time when he instituted the Lord's Supper (Eucharist or Holy Communion).\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 398, \"end\": 403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999981719156, \"rank\": 1.8282721497939644e-09, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.977107696014017, \"rank\": 0.02342069661054414, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While some have tried to claim that this was not a take-off on Leonardo da Vinci's famous painting of the Last Supper, but something from Greek mythology, that seems pretty lame.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.168347972054409e-26, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9999997339023493, \"rank\": 2.660977377609282e-07, \"text\": \"Greek mythology\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the Paris scene, which featured drag queens and children, is juxtaposed with the Da Vinci masterpiece the similarity is striking.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998913154, \"rank\": 1.0887527938988624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.962875880945917e-35, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokeswoman for the International Olympic Committee (IOC) issued a half-hearted 'apology,' stating that it was not intended to mock anything religious and that the IOC is sorry if anyone was offended.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1012, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.841131719043451e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talk about gaslighting!\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These things are in the planning for years so there was lots of time to reflect on how it would come across.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone who thought it would not be seen as blasphemous by the world's Christians must be living in some woke la-la land.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.977107696014017, \"rank\": 0.02342069661054414, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not just the Christian Church that is angered by this display.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1322, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9965497544316155, \"rank\": 0.0034075079303429634, \"text\": \"Christian Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Muslims, who revere Jesus as one of the greatest of the prophets, are also feeling insulted.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.9999855341098228, \"rank\": 1.4466012160077532e-05, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}, {\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999981719156, \"rank\": 1.8282721497939644e-09, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, many non-religious people have expressed disgust at these disrespectful antics.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some have pointed out that that it's anti-woman and also that the hyper-sexualized twerking and gyrating of drag queens is hardly the right atmosphere to bring children into.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the cast actually had a 'wardrobe malfunction' that left his male genitalia exposed!\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When is the world going to say, 'enough is enough'?\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When will people see that this sort of spectacle only hurts your cause?\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When will the IOC and TV networks smarten up?\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.841131719043451e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Answer to that one: when enough advertisers pull their financial support.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We could view this descent into the mire as an expression of cultural suicide.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By mocking Christianity people are turning their backs on our heritage in the Western world.\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999999126873644, \"rank\": 8.731271044524235e-07, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"score\": 0.4850957841955568, \"rank\": 0.8144056215317065, \"text\": \"Western\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christianity had a lot to do with giving us our form of government, our laws, modern science, the status of women, and much more.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999999126873644, \"rank\": 8.731271044524235e-07, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why are we so hell-bent on casting aside the moral wisdom of the last 2,000 years?\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sadly, we will regret the consequences for society if we continue on this course.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 brings to mind Paris 1924, the Olympics in which Eric Liddell, the Scottish sprinter, represented Britain.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2536, \"end\": 2546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0906156008765279e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2562, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999983342605, \"rank\": 1.6656582341219853e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 1924\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2596, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0832373257641677e-46, \"text\": \"Eric Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\"}, {\"begin\": 2614, \"end\": 2622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"score\": 0.9761036082676356, \"rank\": 0.02446861492420057, \"text\": \"Scottish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2645, \"end\": 2652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999782305536149, \"rank\": 0.00016934964354277772, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you remember the movie 'Chariots of Fire' you will recall that Liddell was a deeply committed Christian who, despite the pleadings of powerful people like the Prince of Wales, refused to run in one of the races that was scheduled for a Sunday.\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2720, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"score\": 0.9968512602403157, \"rank\": 0.0030155262789297948, \"text\": \"Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\"}, {\"begin\": 2751, \"end\": 2760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9983852853970262, \"rank\": 0.0016173261229035323, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today's Christians (let alone the unchurched) will have no idea of what the issue was for Liddell.\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.977107696014017, \"rank\": 0.02342069661054414, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2991, \"end\": 2998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"score\": 0.9968512602403157, \"rank\": 0.0030155262789297948, \"text\": \"Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have lost all concept of the Lord's Day or Christian Sabbath, which previous generations took seriously.\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3046, \"end\": 3063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabbath_in_Christianity\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christian Sabbath\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabbath_in_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabbath_in_Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Liddell, Sunday was the day of rest and worship commanded by God in the Ten Commandments (the traditional view of Presbyterians and many other denominations).\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3112, \"end\": 3119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"score\": 0.9968512602403157, \"rank\": 0.0030155262789297948, \"text\": \"Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Liddell\"}, {\"begin\": 3184, \"end\": 3200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0384124897335256e-28, \"text\": \"Ten Commandments\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\"}, {\"begin\": 3226, \"end\": 3239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presbyterianism\", \"score\": 0.9999010231167595, \"rank\": 9.898667357341484e-05, \"text\": \"Presbyterians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presbyterianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presbyterianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He refused to compromise his conscience on the matter.\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He remained true to his convictions and earned the respect of his countrymen.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The sequel is that he went on to become a missionary and died at age 43 in a Japanese internment camp during the Second World War.\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3481, \"end\": 3500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Internment_of_Japanese_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999913072870564, \"rank\": 8.69278873222974e-06, \"text\": \"Japanese internment\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Internment_of_Japanese_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Internment_of_Japanese_Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Interestingly, his widow ended up living in Canada.)\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3580, \"end\": 3586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999998331477539, \"rank\": 1.6682507428977036e-07, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eric Liddell displayed integrity, a character trait that often seems to be in short supply these days.\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3590, \"end\": 3602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0832373257641677e-46, \"text\": \"Eric Liddell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His reverence for God was so strong that he refused to dishonor his name.\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Quite a contrast to what happened in Paris a hundred years later!\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998913154, \"rank\": 1.0887527938988624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"John Vaudry is a retired minister, living in Pembroke.\", \"from\": 3835, \"to\": 3889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3840, \"end\": 3846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaudry\", \"score\": 0.9999999943511284, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaudry\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaudry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaudry\"}, {\"begin\": 3880, \"end\": 3888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"score\": 0.9999999920269147, \"rank\": 7.971899214769902e-09, \"text\": \"Pembroke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Postmedia is committed to maintaining a lively but civil forum for discussion.\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3891, \"end\": 3900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Postmedia\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please keep comments relevant and respectful.\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 4015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Comments may take up to an hour to appear on the site.\", \"from\": 4016, \"to\": 4070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will receive an email if there is a reply to your comment, an update to a thread you follow or if a user you follow comments.\", \"from\": 4071, \"to\": 4200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Visit ourCommunity Guidelinesfor more information.\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"365 Bloor Street East, Toronto, Ontario, M4W 3L4  \\u00a9 2025 Pembroke Observer, a division of Postmedia Network Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 4253, \"to\": 4386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4310, \"end\": 4327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Daily_Observer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pembroke Observer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Daily_Observer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Daily_Observer\"}, {\"begin\": 4343, \"end\": 4365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Postmedia Network Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unauthorized distribution, transmission or republication strictly prohibited.\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This website uses cookies to personalize your content (including ads), and allows us to analyze our traffic.\", \"from\": 4466, \"to\": 4574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more aboutcookies here.\", \"from\": 4575, \"to\": 4603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By continuing to use our site, you agree to ourTerms of UseandPrivacy Policy.\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4681, \"entities\": []}]}"